/*
# Seed APK Store with Categories and Sample Apps

1. Categories (10 total)
- 5 game categories: Action, Arcade, Adventure, Racing, Strategy
- 5 app categories: Tools, Productivity, Social, Entertainment, Education

2. Apps (24 total)
- 12 games and 12 apps with realistic metadata
- Each has icon_url, banner_url (for featured), screenshots, version, file_size, rating, downloads
- download_url points to a placeholder private storage path (never exposed to client)
- checksum is a sample SHA-256 hash for integrity verification demo
- Flags set: is_featured (5), is_trending (8), is_recent (8), is_recommended (8)

3. Security
- No policy changes — uses existing RLS policies from the schema migration.

4. Important Notes
- Uses ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING for idempotency — safe to re-run.
- All image URLs use Pexels stock photos as placeholders.
- download_url values are placeholder paths representing private storage locations.
*/

-- Insert categories
ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;

-- Insert apps (games)
ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;

-- Insert apps (applications)
ON CONFLICT (slug) DO NOTHING;
